public class Spawner extends Object implements dev.kkorolyov.pancake.platform.entity.Component

      Constructs a new spawner.
      Parameters:
      minRadius - radius past which clones are spawned
      maxRadius - radius within which clones are spawned
      interval - minimum seconds between spawns when active; negative implies inactive with abs(interval) interval
      templates - generators of randomly-selected templates to clone and spawn; each template should contain a Position where non-zero position components denote axes to randomize
